{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Hosi's ReaScripts & JSFX for REAPER\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A collection of useful ReaScripts and JSFX plugins for REAPER (https://www.reaper.fm/), created by Hosi Prod.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Installation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This repository is available for installation via ReaPack (https://reapack.com/).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab In REAPER, go to {\f1 Extensions > Reapack > Import repositories...}.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab Paste the following URL into the address field: {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/lachinhan/Hosi-ReaScripts/raw/master/index.xml"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
https://github.com/lachinhan/Hosi-ReaScripts/raw/master/index.xml
}}}
\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 3.\tx360\tab Click {\b OK}.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 4.\tx360\tab Go to {\f1 Extensions > Reapack > Browse packages...}. You can now find, install, and update the scripts and plugins from this repository.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Available Packages\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This repository includes a variety of tools to enhance your workflow.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 ReaScripts\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Freesound Search and Import (ReaImGui):} Search and import sounds directly from Freesound.org.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ... and many other scripts\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 JSFX Plugins\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Hosi Master Limiter:} A mastering limiter combining features from various classic limiters.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Hosi Simple Limiter:} A zero-latency brickwall limiter with gain reduction metering.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b HosiFX Compress:} A simple and effective compressor. *...and many more utility effects including Chorus, Delay, De-esser, EQ, and Reverb.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Usage\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 After installation via ReaPack:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b ReaScripts} can be found and run from the REAPER Action List ({\f1 Actions > Show action list...}).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b JSFX Plugins} will be available in your FX Browser.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Author\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Hosi Prod} ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://github.com/lachinhan"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
lachinhan
}}}
)\sa180\par}
